item.title: About
item.description: Dedicated, Motivated Biomedical Engineer with around 6 years of extensive experience in Hospital fields, as well as in laboratory equipment. Extensive experience in equipment installation, troubleshooting, general maintenance of different makes/models, safety testing, and performance testing of some medical equipment. In addition to, proven expertise in providing quality and timely support by planning, organizing, controlling and coordinating the activities of the Biomedical Engineering Department within the framework of existing policies, procedures and regulatory requirements.
